🚀 How to Run the Project
Step 1: Install Dependencies
pip install pandas openpyxl
Step 2: Run the Python Script
python clean_data.py
Step 3: Check Output
After successful execution, the cleaned dataset will be generated as:
cleaned_dataset.xlsx

This project demonstrates the importance of data cleaning in real-world analytics workflows. By handling missing values, removing duplicates, standardizing formats, and improving data quality, the dataset was successfully transformed into a clean and reliable source for future analysis.